(8, '<p><span lang="EN-US"><a target="_blank" href="http://www.linpin.com.cn/"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:"><span lang="EN-US">环境试验箱</span></span></a></span><span style="font-size:\r\n9.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma">可靠性检测中的可靠性指的是元器件、产品、系统在一定时间内、一定条件下无故障地执行指定功能的能力或可能性。可通过可靠度、失效率、平均无故障间隔产品可靠性。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><strong><span style="font-size:9.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma">环境试验箱</span></strong><span style="font-size:9.0pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma">进行环境可靠性试验是为了保证产品在可使用的寿命期间，在预期的使用，运输和贮存的所有环境下，保持功能可靠性而进行的活动。是将产品暴 露在自然的或人工的环境条件下经受其作用，以评价产品在实际使用，运输和贮存的环境条件下的性能，并分析研究环境因素的影响程度及其作用机理。通过使用各 种环境试验箱模拟气候环境中的高温、低温、高温高湿以及湿度骤变等情况，加速反应产品在使用环境中的状况，来验证其是否达到在研发、设计、制造中预期的质 量目标，从而对产品整体进行评估，以确定产品可靠性寿命。</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:"><img alt="" src="http://www.zgjsq123.com/file/upload/201509/02/10-28-23-93-298.jpg" />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:18.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0"><span style="font-size:\r\n9.0pt">林频讲堂：环境试验箱可靠性检测的必要性<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span><span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp;</span></span>全国免费咨询热线：<span lang="EN-US">4000 662 888</span></span></p>'),
(9, '<p><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:"><span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma">随着航空航天、汽车、家电、科研领域的发展，<strong><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma">高低温交变湿热试验箱</span></strong>得到广泛应用。设备使用次数越多，设备零部件磨损和设备的老化越厉害，进而影响试验的准确性，缩短工作寿命。试验结束后，简单的三步清洁步骤可保设备历久弥新：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma">、排出储水箱剩余的水，避免水箱结垢，使水箱达到延长寿命的作用。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma">、用过的湿球纱布取下，如纱布出现变黄、发硬则直接更换新的湿球纱布；如纱布依然完好可清洁后晾干下次继续使用，不仅节约纱布而且保护湿度传感器；再用干净软布擦拭工作室内的水汽或污渍，如工作室较大不方便手动清洁，也可以直接使用高低温交变湿热试验箱的高温功能，设定</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:">50</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma">度的高温烧烤半小时即可。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma">、打开工作室下方的挡风板（新型设备可直接打开，老式设备需使用梅花起子才能打开），用吸尘器或干抹布将沉淀在上面的灰尘处理干净。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma">注意：清洁最好是在</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:"> </span><span lang="EN-US"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:"><span lang="EN-US">高低温交变湿热试验箱</span></span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma">停止工作半小时之后进行，因制冷系统在使用之后会有一定的温度，以免烫伤操作人员。<br />\r\n<img width="800" height="511" src="http://www.955183.com/file/upload/201509/06/08-10-32-24-45131.jpg" alt="" /><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:"> </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0"><span lang="EN-US"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:"><span lang="EN-US">清洁三部曲，高低温交变湿热试验箱换新颜</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt"><span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span><span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt">全国免费咨询热线：<span lang="EN-US">4000 662 888</span></span></p>'),
(10, '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;mso-ascii&nbsp;-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma">一般来讲，<strong><span style="font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii&nbsp;-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma">高低温试验箱</span></strong>对运作的时间及温度都有非常严格的规定，为保证试验的准确性，其运作都会按照其规定的范围进行。但是这些规定都会由于高低温试验箱操作者使用的不当而造成降温缓慢，那么造成此现象的解决办法又是哪些呢？今天就由小编一一为你道来：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; a</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;mso-ascii&nbsp;-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma">）为保证试验的正常运行，应当定期清理冷凝器，确保冷凝器上没有多余的杂质；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; b</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;mso-ascii&nbsp;-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma">）在</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:"> </span><span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://www.linpin.com.cn/" target="_blank"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:"><span lang="EN-US">高低温试验箱</span></span></a></span><span style="font-size:\r\n9.0pt;mso-ascii&nbsp;-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma">所在的实验室应当保证有着良好的通风，有条件的还可在实验室内安装空调来达到设备对温度的要求，如若发现实验室内的温度过高，可直接打开下面挡板用风扇吹，从而达到降温的效果；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; c</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;mso-ascii&nbsp;-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma">）负载过大也可造成设备的不制冷，所以在试验之前，理应检查试验工件是否是带电测试，并测出带电测试时工件的发热量，如发热量在</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:">300W</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;mso-ascii&nbsp;-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma">以内对于试验箱没有影响，但是发热量过大会使箱内温度降温缓慢无法达到设备的设定置或不制冷；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; d</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;mso-ascii&nbsp;-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma">）确保风机的正常运行，在高低温试验箱的运行中，如发现风机无法正常启动。应当立即停止运作，进行检修，否则会给带来损害，所以为了确保试验的正常运行，一定要等解决掉问题后，再进行使用；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; e</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;mso-ascii&nbsp;-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma">）高低温试验箱的温度下降很慢的主要原因是制冷的问题，该设备的制冷系统一旦出现问题，那么就会造成温度下降很慢。所以在试验前，应当检查高低温试验箱的制冷系统，首先检查两组制冷机组的低温</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:">(R23)</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;mso-ascii&nbsp;-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma">级压缩机的排气和吸气压力都较正常值偏低，而且吸气压力呈抽空状态，说明主制冷机组的制冷剂量不足。用手摸主机组</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:">R23</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;mso-ascii&nbsp;-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma">压缩机的排气和吸气管路，发现排气管路的温度不高，吸气管路的温度也不低</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:">(</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;mso-ascii&nbsp;-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma">未结霜</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;\r\nfont-family:">)</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;\r\nmso-ascii&nbsp;-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma">，这也说明了主机组的</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\r\n">R23</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;mso-ascii&nbsp;-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma">制冷剂不足。<br />\r\n<img width="800" height="511" alt="" src="http://zsspw.net/file/upload/201509/09/08-41-18-75-150.jpg" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0"><span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://www.linpin.com.cn/ViewInfo-2122.html"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:"><span lang="EN-US">高低温试验箱降温缓慢的解决方案</span></span></a></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt"><span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span><span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt">全国免费咨询热线：<span lang="EN-US">4000 662 888</span></span></p>');
