></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">并且在高新技术领域中对于</span><span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://www.linpin.com/"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:\r\n9.0pt;font-family:&quot;宋体,Verdana,Arial&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;"><span lang="EN-US">恒温恒湿箱</span></span></a></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">的要求相较于其他行业更加苛刻，质量的可靠性、设备的维护管理费用等，这些对于工业中批量生产产品的企业都是相当重要的。在医药方面，用于药品，试剂的储存，运输等，由以上可以明显的看出该设备的重要性。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt">&nbsp;<img src="http://www.gefee.com/file/upload/201511/06/14-16-02-67-952.jpg" alt="2 恒温恒湿-高低温交湿  10-15 张左右8" /></span></p>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;\r\nmso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">恒温恒湿箱遍布各大高新技术行业</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:\r\nZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA"><span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:\r\nZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">全国免费咨询热线：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:\r\nZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">4000 662 8</span>'),
(12, '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi">恒温恒湿试验箱</span></strong><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">是需要对进行检测的材料在耐湿的环境下的一款检测设备，所以水是一定会用到的，是不可避免的。但是水质的优劣都会时刻影响到设备，严重的话可能会对设备造成损害，所以用水需谨慎，不然会得不偿失。以下来做一个对比，让每一位用户思考一下以后硬要使用什么样的水是最佳的。</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">其实用一般自来水是可以的，但是如果用绝缘性更好的水则是最佳的。自来水的湿度效果可以达到试验箱的需求，但如果长期用自来水做湿度用水，水管中很容易生</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt"> </span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">出水垢，而且自来水中的杂质还会吸附到产品表面，水箱也会不干净，所以会导致试验箱出现故障。可是当你使用纯净水或蒸馏水，再设制回水再利用，成本也不会</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt"> </span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">消耗太大，对水管、水箱、水路等都比较好，也不会造成湿度传感器的短路。当然，如果你可以勤换、勤洗自然水当然也是不会造成对设备太大的伤害。</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">但是只要用户在选择</span><span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://www.linpin.com/"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:\r\n9.0pt;font-family:&quot;宋体,Verdana,Arial&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;"><span lang="EN-US">恒温恒湿试验箱</span></span></a></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">厂家的时候，可以咨询厂家是否能安装自然水过滤系统，过滤后自然水也可以转化成纯净水，所以选择一个优质放心的厂家也是关键的所在。</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt">&nbsp;<img width="615" height="386" src="http://www.cnfmw.cn/file/upload/201511/10/10-21-18-53-5118.jpg" alt="" /></span></p>\r\n<p align="left" style="text-align:left;text-indent:13.5pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:1.5"><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 恒温恒湿试验箱使用水规定</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt"><span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp;</span><span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">全国免费咨询热线：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt">4000 662 888</span></p>'),
(13, '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">　<strong><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi">恒温恒湿箱</span></strong>的制冷系统是必不可少的，完善制冷系统需要很多的配件，但是有一些用户会去怀疑这么多的配件到底是否全部都有用，还是有一些只是起到装饰作用，多了无益，也不必浪费这些钱。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">　　热交换器它有三个好处，一个可以使冷凝的制冷剂过冷，二是可以换回气制冷剂充分气化，三是可以提高系统功效，它可以减少提前气化量和夜击风险，</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt"> </span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">但是热交换器的接入较为复杂</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt">;</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">在循环支路回气口加上止逆阀，可以防止制冷器回流在多个循环支路里积载，循环空间减少，但考虑到防止液态积聚也有没有加上止</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt"> </span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">逆阀：气液分离器是避免液击的有效手段之一，同时还可以适当调节制冷量，但是气液分离器同时也切断了系统回油</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt">;</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">积液器是使制冷系统中未冷凝的制冷剂不进入</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt"> </span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">或少进入循环系统，提高换热效率，但同时会带来制冷剂充注量增加，冷凝压力偏低的问题。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">　　</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt"><a href="http://www.linpin.com/"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;宋体,Verdana,Arial&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;"><span lang="EN-US">恒温恒湿箱</span></span></a></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">制冷系统上的配件都是有利端也有弊端，所以用户可以考虑到自身需求去选择够买试验箱，最好可以选择能为您量身定做的厂家，这样更为贴心方便去满足您的需求，无需您担心配件给您带去顾虑和浪费。</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt">&nbsp;<img width="800" height="476" src="http://zsspw.net/file/upload/201511/12/10-19-17-60-150.jpg" alt="" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-